,"msg":"你同佢識咗耐唔耐？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T10:14:12.000Z","msg":"識咗一年"},{"pid":"2cbf45410617a06ecca7592ab8c666bcfd0d313c","tid":840363,"uid":211925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T10:19:07.000Z","msg":"i know that feel <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390dc07a7722d1ec1a9c697e09880c991000f269","tid":840363,"uid":201211,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"553e6c2ed6793509fb4fb4f2112cbb61ab74bbd4","tid":840363,"uid":204481,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"33d1e7ea317674409c93c59934ee3ce78f67ec7d","tid":840363,"uid":204481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T01:07:43.000Z","msg":"但你太自愛 我卻連自己都不去愛<br />\n<br />\n我都係一樣情況，已選擇放棄。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T01:09:44.000Z","msg":"但放棄左仲要日夜相見都大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 次次見到個心都會嗱住嗱住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T10:21:52.000Z","msg":"依家就系咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 救命<br />\n系會搞到你開始懷疑自己然後唔敢再去愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9fd465aa9847d2c99a0070d919e6fa453e13e3","tid":840363,"uid":124163,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T10:24:38.000Z","msg":"咁唔係話你做得多野就要鍾意你架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你覺得同人地好夾姐，但可能人地真係對你冇興趣/你唔係佢鍾意嘅類型<br />\n<br />\n佢同你分清楚已經好好，係你自己不斷ff同強求，怪得邊個"},{"pid":"33e8e4a4060943c6d0c2bd72d8319ebb215a87b4","tid":840363,"uid":213412,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"你揀個女人會回應你好過而家甘辛苦啦。block 9 左佢。1年後好快冇事。咩叫講唔洗又係到享受你接收工既服務。5鐘意就拒絕你啦。你傻仔係到俾人蝦"},{"pid":"2a0b51c13e1b21d51d99a503a700188f21233263","tid":840363,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T10:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/182937_0a7d91282e702a986392df63b92b3b90.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F182937_0a7d91282e702a986392df63b92b3b90.gif&h=fd9051ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1aed79ef6450d112e9f0257a5aff1e7c29b3e41a","tid":840363,"uid":124163,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T10:30:55.000Z","msg":"如果咁就話唔再相信愛情，會唔會太搞笑，因為愛情根本冇出現過<br />\n<br />\n而家係你搵錯對象去愛，搵啱對象其實自自然然會互相希望起埋一齊"},{"pid":"e74ebb6ec8857e7c256bf6d8ea9db8e37f1e9b2f","tid":840363,"uid":142979,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T18:51:30.000Z","msg":"最唔甘心既係 明明係佢撩我先...<br />\n如果對我冇心點解要黎搞9我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由我平平淡淡一個人咪算"},{"pid":"5311482320cde399006d4706c9af0a7e3904403e","tid":840363,"uid":76587,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T18:53:49.000Z","msg":"鍾意一個人係唔辛苦<br />\n<br />\n鍾意個唔鍾意你嘅人先最辛苦"},{"pid":"98dfd9289ab19c4113b7bfcdcf3944cd355b5ffd","tid":840363,"uid":71085,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T20:18:17.000Z","msg":"我以為係自己出文<br />\n去番同佢去過嘅地方就會諗起同佢一齊發生過嘅事、講過嘅話題<br />\n好掛住佢，好想見到佢<br />\n但我咩都唔係<br />\n點解每次都要鍾意啲唔鍾意自己嘅人？<br />\n好犯賤"},{"pid":"ccd933e71b3cdb2fd642f1486404d881aa0ff93a","tid":840363,"uid":71085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"390dc07a7722d1ec1a9c697e09880c991000f269","tid":840363,"uid":201211,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"553e6c2ed6793509fb4fb4f2112cbb61ab74bbd4","tid":840363,"uid":204481,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"33d1e7ea317674409c93c59934ee3ce78f67ec7d","tid":840363,"uid":204481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T01:07:43.000Z","msg":"但你太自愛 我卻連自己都不去愛<br />\n<br />\n我都係一樣情況，已選擇放棄。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T01:09:44.000Z","msg":"但放棄左仲要日夜相見都大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 次次見到個心都會嗱住嗱住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T10:21:52.000Z","msg":"依家就系咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 救命<br />\n系會搞到你開始懷疑自己然後唔敢再去愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T20:19:41.000Z","msg":"系你老母<br />\n叫春還叫春，打番正字，睇得好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d336912a5c38d6034c0de7411aaa7ed3d2037e5","tid":840363,"uid":25170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T20:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de519aa394d27ba92011a1d737fdc6807f2eb45","tid":840363,"uid":96979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T21:14:19.000Z","msg":"我係唔知我同佢乜關係啊屌<br />\n講普通朋友 唔係<br />\n講情侶 唔係<br />\n拖手有 攬有<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ed6fde100999ef42203673e78be63be3d1f655","tid":840363,"uid":42900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T21:40:09.000Z","msg":"理智，ok?"}]}